channel.title: Buying Quality Scripts, Flax Picker,Spinner and Banker and others
channel.description:
I've come to the realization that I just can't get the hang of Scripting, So for now, I'm going to leave it up to the many other talented individuals here...I have a few ideas I would like to work on someone with, but here is some basic ones that I am looking for right now, that I'm pretty sure are out there....these will be for my own private use and not for resale, Please either post here with prices or email me at RAM_RUNE@hotmail.com, Also, if it is a very reliable and original script, I may be interested in giving portions of the materials I gather.....Thanks [b]RAM[/b]
[ul][li] Flax Picker, Spinner and Banker Varrock Yew Cutter and Banker Karamja Lobby Fisher and Banker Rune Crafters, particulary Natures Seaweed gathers Lumby Cowhide gather and Banker Shiloh Village gemstone miner and Banker Zammy wine Telegrabber and Banker Chaos druid herb collector and banker Alkarid herb collector and Banker "Between a rock" Goldminer and Banker Alkarid Miner and banker[/li] [li][/li][/ul]
These are just a few, the ones at the top i am looking for asap.....
